Package: rstats
Type: Package
Title: R package usage statistics
Version: 0.11
Date: 2013-04-16
Author: Zhiyong Zhang
Maintainer: Zhiyong Zhang <johnnyzhz@gmail.com>
Suggests: RCurl
Description: Usage statistics about a package can help its developers, and ultimately its users, in many ways. However, such information is rarely available. The package rstats is developed to better collect and utilize package usage statistics. The package allow users to share download information, rate, comment, and ask questions on a package within R directly. The packages sends the information to the package developer directly and also allows other users to repsond to it.
License: GPL
Packaged: 2013-05-29 13:08:01 UTC; zzhang4
